            "heading": "About Hansgrohe",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_XWFjiJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Hansgrohe is one of the world’s leading manufacturers of bathroom and kitchen fixtures, with over a century of excellence in design and performance. Headquartered in Schiltach, Germany, the Hansgrohe Group creates products that bring water to life through thoughtful engineering, aesthetic appeal and environmental responsibility. </p><p>At Hansgrohe, water isn’t just a resource; it's the core of user experience. Their mission is to deliver meaningful, water-rich interactions, whether it’s a morning shower or a kitchen rinse. </p><p>Over the years, Hansgrohe has partnered with top design studios (including Phoenix Design) to refine their form language and visual identity. </p><p>In Australia, we stock the full Hansgrohe range; backed by local support, warranty servicing, and spare parts availability.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
