    "multicolumn_DmjYfM": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_dpQBDC": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/72800003_Lifestyle2_Web_6780cc3a-8eb8-4b6b-a22f-67b8ab4a8b04.jpg",
            "title": "Tapware",
            "text": "<p>Discover Hansgrohe Tapware, a leader in luxury kitchen and bathroom fittings designed for discerning Australian homes. Hansgrohe combines sophisticated German engineering with contemporary style, offering an extensive range of basin mixers, kitchen taps, and accessories that elevate any renovation or new build. Renowned for innovation, water efficiency, and precision craftsmanship, Hansgrohe tapware delivers the performance and durability that homeowners and designers rely on. Whether you’re refreshing your kitchen with a sleek mixer or upgrading your bathroom with a refined basin tap, Hansgrohe provides stylish, high-quality solutions that blend form with function. At Cook & Bathe, we proudly stock Hansgrohe’s best-selling tapware collections, helping you find the perfect balance between modern design and everyday practicality. Explore Hansgrohe Tapware today to bring elegance and performance to your kitchen and bathroom.</p>",
            "link_label": "Hansgrohe Tapware",
            "link": "shopify://collections/hansgrohe-tapware"
          }
        },
        "column_btBdt3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/banner_hansgrohesinkmixers_1080x594_0dbdc946-e254-4969-b0d4-dcbc754a6fde.jpg",
            "title": "Sink Mixers",
            "text": "<p>Experience the craftsmanship and design of Hansgrohe Sink Mixers, engineered to bring comfort and performance to your kitchen. Hansgrohe delivers a sophisticated selection of kitchen mixers and pull-out taps that combine timeless design with innovative water-saving technology. Built to meet the highest standards of German precision, Hansgrohe mixers offer smooth operation, sustainable efficiency, and a refined aesthetic that complements any interior. Whether you’re upgrading a family kitchen or creating a designer space, Hansgrohe’s sink mixers provide practical functionality, effortless control, and lasting reliability. At Cook & Bathe, we curate a premium selection of Hansgrohe’s best-selling mixers, allowing you to enjoy precision water flow and elegant form every day. Explore Hansgrohe Sink Mixers today and discover the perfect blend of beauty and performance for your kitchen.</p>",
            "link_label": "Hansgrohe Sink Mixers",
            "link": "shopify://collections/hansgrohe-sink-mixers"
          }
        },
        "column_JE3UyW": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/24141700_Lifestyle1_Web_0c541362-b704-422b-b6b2-203218c54fed.jpg",
            "title": "Showers",
            "text": "<p>Discover the innovation and indulgence of Hansgrohe Showers, meticulously designed to transform your bathroom into a sanctuary of comfort and style. Hansgrohe offers a range of premium overhead, rail, and hand showers crafted with cutting-edge features such as AirPower, Select, and EcoSmart technologies that redefine the shower experience. Combining refined aesthetics with functional brilliance, Hansgrohe showers deliver powerful performance while reducing water consumption — ideal for the modern Australian home. Whether you’re renovating your ensuite or upgrading a family bathroom, Hansgrohe provides luxurious, reliable solutions that inspire daily relaxation. At Cook & Bathe, we proudly feature Hansgrohe’s most sought-after shower collections, helping you create a space that is both sustainable and sophisticated. Explore Hansgrohe Showers today and experience the perfect harmony of design, technology, and comfort.</p>",
            "link_label": "Hansgrohe Showers",
            "link": "shopify://collections/hansgrohe-showers"
          }
        }
      },
