        "heading_AwwJPb": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Hansgrohe Croma Range",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_f7r6Up": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Discover the <strong>Hansgrohe Croma Range</strong>, where German engineering meets everyday practicality to transform your daily routine in Australian bathrooms.</p><p>With its <strong>sleek design</strong> and versatile functionality, the Croma collection combines premium form with smart features, delivering exceptional shower performance. Featuring <strong>innovative water-saving technology</strong> and durable finishes, this collection includes everything from ergonomic hand showers to indulgent, full-coverage overheads.</p><p>Ideal for homeowners seeking a sophisticated aesthetic without compromising on efficiency or reliability, Croma provides intuitive controls and quality components that seamlessly integrate with both contemporary and classic bathroom styles. Explore the curated <strong>Hansgrohe Croma</strong> collection at <strong>Cook & Bathe</strong> and elevate your shower space with trusted German excellence.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_kmzfDg": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
