        "text_6WzHiT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Discover the Hansgrohe Crometta range, your affordable entry point to German shower innovation and quality. With its clean, contemporary aesthetic and proven performance, Crometta delivers an invigorating and efficient shower experience every day.</p><p>Featuring water-saving **EcoSmart** technology and durable chrome finishes, this collection includes versatile hand showers and all-in-one **Showerpipe** systems, perfect for upgrading your bathroom without complex renovations. Crometta is the smart, reliable choice for homeowners seeking sophisticated style that doesn't compromise on efficiency or price.</p><p>Explore the full Crometta collection at Cook & Bathe and elevate your daily routine with reliable, eco-conscious shower technology.</p>",
